Notes: WIAC tournament quarterfinal...SP will host UW-Oshkosh in semifinals Wed. at
7 pm...SP's Scott scores 10 of team's first 13 points, finishing with season
high 19 points...SP trailed 42-40 with 14:14 left before a 12-0 run over next
four minutes...SP advances to semifinals for fifth straight year.
